cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software in academic work, please cite it as below."
title: "open-data-assistant-config (lumi-assistant): an opencode configuration for ATLAS Open Data and CERN Open Data"
abstract: >
  A configuration bundle for the opencode / lumi agent CLI, providing
  intent-organised skills, sub-agent personas, remote MCP wiring
  (atlasopenmagic, cernopendata) and CVMFS-deployable packaging for
  ATLAS Open Data and broader CERN Open Data workflows on Binder,
  Colab, SWAN, lxplus, and local Jupyter installs.
type: software
authors:
